Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Chrysler repays loan
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043x8p4
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 17 Jul 1983
Chrysler startles US by repaying government bail-out loan in record time. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.